        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Some Borg-Warner SA75 fan drives, International Code 12TSV, used on T 444E engines may not engage
                    at the correct temperature and/or engine RPM. These fan drives were used in 1000, 3400, 3800, IC
                    Bus, and 4700 Models built between August 9, 2000 and October 4, 2000.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
